{"type":"message","id":"12674a26","parentId":"7f1766d5","timestamp":"2026-04-02T07:14:19.474Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_86b3a2a13db34b8191debeda","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 航空公司列表配置\n\n## 使用说明\n\n本文件包含所有需要搜索的航空公司配置，按优先级分组：\n- **P0**: 核心关注航司 (必须深度搜索)\n- **P1**: 重点航司 (亚洲廉航 + 中东土豪航)\n- **P2**: 其他航司 (欧美航司 + 其他全服务航司)\n\n## P0 核心关注\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"Thai Lion Air\",\n  \"cn_name\": \"泰国狮航\",\n  \"keywords\": [\"Thai Lion Air\", \"泰国狮航\", \"泰狮航\"],\n  \"priority\": 0,\n  \"website\": \"https://www.lionairthai.com/\"\n}\n```\n\n## P1 重点航司\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"AirAsia\",\n  \"cn_name\": \"亚洲航空\",\n  \"keywords\": [\"AirAsia\", \"亚航\", \"亚洲航空\"],\n  \"priority\": 1,\n  \"website\": \"https://www.airasia.com/\"\n}\n```\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"Cebu Pacific\",\n  \"cn_name\": \"宿务航空\",\n  \"keywords\": [\"Cebu Pacific\", \"宿务航空\", \"宿雾航空\"],\n  \"priority\": 1,\n  \"website\": \"https://www.cebupacificair.com/\"\n}\n```\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"IndiGo\",\n  \"cn_name\": \"靛蓝航空\",\n  \"keywords\": [\"IndiGo\", \"靛蓝航空\", \"印地高航空\"],\n  \"priority\": 1,\n  \"website\": \"https://www.goindigo.in/\"\n}\n```\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"HK Express\",\n  \"cn_name\": \"香港快运\",\n  \"keywords\": [\"HK Express\", \"香港快运\"],\n  \"priority\": 1,\n  \"website\": \"https://www.hkexpress.com/\"\n}\n```\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"VietJet Air\",\n  \"cn_name\": \"越捷航空\",\n  \"keywords\": [\"VietJet Air\", \"越捷航空\"],\n  \"priority\": 1,\n  \"website\": \"https://www.vietjetair.com/\"\n}\n```\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"Emirates\",\n  \"cn_name\": \"阿联酋航空\",\n  \"keywords\": [\"Emirates\", \"阿联酋航空\"],\n  \"priority\": 1,\n  \"website\": \"https://www.emirates.com/\"\n}\n```\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"Qatar Airways\",\n  \"cn_name\": \"卡塔尔航空\",\n  \"keywords\": [\"Qatar Airways\", \"卡塔尔航空\"],\n  \"priority\": 1,\n  \"website\": \"https://www.qatarairways.com/\"\n}\n```\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"Turkish Airlines\",\n  \"cn_name\": \"土耳其航空\",\n  \"keywords\": [\"Turkish Airlines\", \"土耳其航空\"],\n  \"priority\": 1,\n  \"website\": \"https://www.turkishairlines.com/\"\n}\n```\n\n## P2 其他航司\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"EVA Air\",\n  \"cn_name\": \"长荣航空\",\n  \"keywords\": [\"EVA Air\", \"长荣航空\"],\n  \"priority\": 2,\n  \"website\": \"https://www.evaair.com/\"\n}\n```\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"China Airlines\",\n  \"cn_name\": \"中华航空\",\n  \"keywords\": [\"China Airlines\", \"中华航空\", \"华航\"],\n  \"priority\": 2,\n  \"website\": \"https://www.china-airlines.com/\"\n}\n```\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"Vietnam Airlines\",\n  \"cn_name\": \"越南航空\",\n  \"keywords\": [\"Vietnam Airlines\", \"越南航空\"],\n  \"priority\": 2,\n  \"website\": \"https://www.vietnamairlines.com/\"\n}\n```\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"Singapore Airlines\",\n  \"cn_name\": \"新加坡航空\",\n  \"keywords\": [\"Singapore Airlines\", \"新航\", \"新加坡航空\"],\n  \"priority\": 2,\n  \"website\": \"https://www.singaporeair.com/\"\n}\n```\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"Cathay Pacific\",\n  \"cn_name\": \"国泰航空\",\n  \"keywords\": [\"Cathay Pacific\", \"国泰航空\"],\n  \"priority\": 2,\n  \"website\": \"https://www.cathaypacific.com/\"\n}\n```\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"JAL\",\n  \"cn_name\": \"日本航空\",\n  \"keywords\": [\"JAL\", \"日本航空\", \"Japan Airlines\"],\n  \"priority\": 2,\n  \"website\": \"https://www.jal.co.jp/\"\n}\n```\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"ANA\",\n  \"cn_name\": \"全日空\",\n  \"keywords\": [\"ANA\", \"全日空\"],\n  \"priority\": 2,\n  \"website\": \"https://www.ana.co.jp/\"\n}\n```\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"Korean Air\",\n  \"cn_name\": \"大韩航空\",\n  \"keywords\": [\"Korean Air\", \"大韩航空\"],\n  \"priority\": 2,\n  \"website\": \"https://www.koreanair.com/\"\n}\n```\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"Flair Airlines\",\n  \"cn_name\": \"弗莱尔航空\",\n  \"keywords\": [\"Flair Airlines\", \"弗莱尔航空\"],\n  \"priority\": 2,\n  \"website\": \"https://flyflair.com/\"\n}\n```\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"Wizz Air\",\n  \"cn_name\": \"威兹航空\",\n  \"keywords\": [\"Wizz Air\", \"威兹航空\"],\n  \"priority\": 2,\n  \"website\": \"https://wizzair.com/\"\n}\n```\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"Spirit Airlines\",\n  \"cn_name\": \"精神航空\",\n  \"keywords\": [\"Spirit Airlines\", \"精神航空\"],\n  \"priority\": 2,\n  \"website\": \"https://www.spirit.com/\"\n}\n```\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"Volaris\",\n  \"cn_name\": \"沃拉里斯航空\",\n  \"keywords\": [\"Volaris\", \"沃拉里斯航空\"],\n  \"priority\": 2,\n  \"website\": \"https://www.volaris.com/\"\n}\n```\n\n## 统计\n\n- **P0**: 1 家\n- **P1**: 8 家\n- **P2**: 12 家\n- **总计**: 21 家\n\n## 添加新航司\n\n如需添加新航司，请按以下格式添加到对应优先级分组：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"航空司英文名\",\n  \"cn_name\": \"航空公司中文名\",\n  \"keywords\": [\"英文名\", \"中文名\", \"别名\"],\n  \"priority\": 1,\n  \"website\": \"https://官网链接/\"\n}\n```\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775114059469}}
